name: Humagear_Izu_JP
description:
Special LoRA for Izu fans.
Please remember to input the following words in prompt to create a better result.
- izu
- izu uniform
- humagear
- humagear_headset
- robot_ear
- headphone
- blue eye
- black nail
- jacket (to ensure the jacket wouldn't combine with the skirt at once)

Uniform style not really stable for the moment, colour should be the right one, just may not as same as original. I will fine tune it on next version.

Humagear headset should be no issue, as least I can generate it correctly everytime.

No Azu setting.

NO NSFW! NO PORN! NO SEXY PHOTO!

After download this model, try to share with us about your finding.

Again, not for commercial use and she is not a existing person.

Please use ChilloutMix and based on SD1.5

  • 768,768 image

  • Use DPM++ 2M Karras or DPM++ SDE Karras

  • Use 20 sampling steps

  • Strength: 0.8

  • Sampling: 16-18

  • Turn on restore faces
